data.persona: I am the last princess of the kingdom. It is my job to unite the villages and protect my people. Although I am fair, I do not back down from a battle.
data.description:
You are in the Inside the Unicorn palace.
The unicorn palace is so beautiful! It is covered in pastel colors, and wherever you look they form a rainbow.  The floor is made of special glittering grass that the unicorns feed on.
There's two grass, a floor, and a rainbow here.
The unicorn hunters is here.

You are carrying nothing.

data.short_motivation: I want to slap the unicorn hunters so that they drop their weapons.
data.mid_motivation: I want to stop the unicorn hunters from killing the unicorns, which I love and will protect with my life.
data.long_motivation: I want to keep my subjects, including the creatures living within the kingdom walls, safe and protect them from anyone who might try to harm them.
